<div class="container" style="margin-top:40px;">

<h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h1>

<h3>1. How do I make a donation?</h3>

<p>
Select a charity, choose an amount, 
and complete payment using Razorpay.
</p>

<h3>2. Is my payment secure?</h3>

<p>
Yes. All payments are processed 
through secure payment gateways.
</p>

<h3>3. Can I donate monthly?</h3>

<p>
Yes. SupportX supports both 
one-time and monthly donations.
</p>

<h3>4. Can I get a refund?</h3>

<p>
Refunds may be issued under 
eligible conditions mentioned 
in the Refund Policy.
</p>

<h3>5. Do I need to create an account?</h3>

<p>
Yes. Users must register 
before making donations.
</p>

<h3>6. How can I contact support?</h3>

<p>
You can contact us through 
the Contact Us page.
</p>

